Since $\angle PQS = 60^\circ$ and $PQ = 12,$ the area of sector $PQS$ is
\[\frac{1}{6} \cdot 12^2 \cdot \pi = 24 \pi.\]Also, triangle $PQS$ is equilateral with side length 12, so its area is
